        public static double ascvd10Year​(Person person,
                                 long time,
                                 boolean perTimestep)
        Calculates the 10-year ASCVD Risk Estimates, based on the Pooled Cohort Equations for Estimation of 10-Year Risk of Hard ASCVD. https://doi.org/10.1161/01.cir.0000437741.48606.98
        Parameters:
        person - The patient.
        time - Time to calculate risk as of
        perTimestep - Whether to return the risk per timestep (default 7 days) or per 10 years
        Returns:
        the patient's ASCVD risk score
